name=Spongie's Open Jackets - B42.19 Fix
id=SpongieOpenJacketsB42Fix
author=Kriz999
require=SpnOpenCloth
pzversion=42.19
versionMin=42.19.0
description=Stops the "Not in debug" / "expected 2 arguments, got 1" / "unhideModel of non-table: null" error spam from Spongie's Open Jackets on Build 42.19.0, and makes the open-jacket layering actually work again. The mod's BodyLocations tweaker used the getClassField/getClassFieldVal reflection helpers, which now throw outside -debug; this patch rebuilds the Human body-location group without reflection. Requires Spongie's Open Jackets. ENABLE AFTER Spongie's Open Jackets.
